<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hunter" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hunter,</orth> 1) one pursuing and chasing wild animals, a huntsman: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.4.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 4, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.4.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 4, 28</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.31" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.31" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 31</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.31" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 31</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.259" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 259</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.243" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 243</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 2, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 2, 5</bibl> <bibl n="shak. jc 3.1.205" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. III, 1, 205</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.3.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 3, 74</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.3.39" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 39</bibl>. With <emph>for</emph>: <cit><quote>I'll play the h. for thy life,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 1, 17</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) a dog employed in the chase: <bibl n="shak. mac 3.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 1, 97</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>